    <Content contentid="632" contenttypeid="INTRO" desc="Introduction">
      <Description><![CDATA[<p> Absorb the energy and be soothed by the serenity of the <span style="font-style: italic;">Island of Gods</span> in exotic splendour at Villa Asmara.&nbsp; This enchanting rural sanctuary overlooks the rice fields and rugged shores of the sleepy village of Cemagi that worships its very own sea temple, Pura Gede Luhur Batungaus.</p><p> Featuring an open-sided lounge and dining room, large swimming pool, games room, media room and four spacious bedrooms with ensuite garden bathrooms, this fully staffed villa is the ideal choice for families and friends craving peace and privacy. <br /></p>]]></Description>
